Interface AmpRequiredComponentContainer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AmpActivityBudgetExtrasPanel, AmpAidEffectivenessFormSectionFeature, AmpDonorFundingFormSectionFeature, AmpDonorFundingInfoSubsectionFeature, AmpFundingSummaryPanel, AmpIdentificationFormSectionFeature, AmpIssuesFormSectionFeature, AmpLineMinistryObservationsFormSectionFeature, AmpLoanDetailsSubsectionFeature, AmpOverviewSection, AmpPlanningFormSectionFeature, AmpProjectCost, AmpProposedProjectCost, AmpRegionalObservationsFormSectionFeature

    public interface AmpRequiredComponentContainer
    Marker interface for getting the FormComponents that will be required in a panel. All AMP panels that contain fields that should be made required/not required when 'saving as draft' or 'submit and save' must implement this interface
